OL,3,C'It would be devastating': Family
OL,4,Cissue plea to keep day care centre open
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports journalist Emma
OL,7,FSweeney spoke to Mark Hilton's family
OL,8,Fabout the potential closure of the
OL,9,Fcentre
OL,11,FA day care service for adults with
OL,12,Flearning difficulties is facing
OL,13,Fclosure - as a council looks to save
OL,14,Fmoney and release itself from debt.
OL,16,FMark Hilton has attended the centre in
OL,17,FChadderton Park, in Oldham, for 20
OL,18,Fyears, but his family members fear any
OL,19,Fclosure will be devastating for not
OL,20,Fonly him, but also other users who
OL,21,Frely on the service.
