OL,3,C'It would be devastating': Family
OL,4,Cissue plea to keep day care centre open
OL,6,FThe 50-year-old is non-verbal with
OL,7,Fprofound Autism, and goes to the day
OL,8,Fcare centre five days a week.
OL,10,F"When we found out I was just
OL,11,Fdisgusted, really disgusted. I just
OL,12,Fcan't imagine Mark not attending
OL,13,FChadderton Park," his sister, Amanda
OL,14,FShelley, said.
OL,16,FHis dad, John Hilton, added: "The
OL,17,Fstaff are so caring interacting with
OL,18,FMark, he feels that."
