OL,3,C'It would be devastating': Family
OL,4,Cissue plea to keep day care centre open
OL,6,FThe day care centre provides "an
OL,7,Falternative to traditional daycare"
OL,8,Faccording to the Oldham Council
OL,9,Fwebsite.
OL,11,FAmanda, who also acts as Mark's
OL,12,Fpersonal assistant for 15 hours a
OL,13,Fweek, says he loves playing music,
OL,14,Fwoodworking, and gardening at the
OL,15,Fcentre.
OL,17,F"All our plants are from there because
OL,18,Fthey grow them themselves," she said.
