OL,3,C'It would be devastating': Family
OL,4,Cissue plea to keep day care centre open
OL,6,FMark likes familiarity and routine,
OL,7,Fand his family say the day care centre
OL,8,Fhas been his world for two decades.
OL,10,FJohn said Mark struggles with change:
OL,11,F"A year ago when Mark's medication
OL,12,Fchanged it was impossible to get any
OL,13,Fcommunication with him whatsoever."
OL,15,FWith a potential closure, that
OL,16,Fcertainty is now under threat.
OL,18,F"It would be devastating for him to be
OL,19,Ftaken out of that environment because
OL,20,Fit's a big part of his life," John
OL,21,Fsaid.
