OL,3,C'It would be devastating': Family
OL,4,Cissue plea to keep day care centre open
OL,6,FOldham Council says it has to cut #8
OL,7,Fmillion in order to balance its books
OL,8,Fand currently adult social care is one
OL,9,Fof its biggest costs at #8.9 million.
OL,11,FIt proposed closing Chadderton Park,
OL,12,Fwhich costs #150,000 to run, in its
OL,13,Fbudget report. The centre supports 21
OL,14,Fadults with complex needs.
OL,16,FThe local authority says it is also no
OL,17,Flonger giving care workers the
OL,18,FNational Living Wage pay rise planned
OL,19,F- saving the council more than #2
OL,20,Fmillion.
