OL,3,C'It would be devastating': Family
OL,4,Cissue plea to keep day care centre open
OL,6,FBut the council say no final decision
OL,7,Fhas yet been made - and there are
OL,8,Fother places locally people could go
OL,9,Fto.
OL,11,FAmanda issued a final plea: "Just
OL,12,Fplease keep the centre open for the
OL,13,Flives and wellbeing of these adults,
OL,14,Fthey are beautiful adults that just
OL,15,Fneed some support from everybody. They
OL,16,Fneed it. We need it."
