OL,3,C'It would be devastating': Family
OL,4,Cissue plea to keep day care centre open
OL,6,FCouncillor Barbara Brownridge, Cabinet
OL,7,FMember for Adults, Health and
OL,8,FWellbeing, said: "I want to reassure
OL,9,Fpeople that no final decision has been
OL,10,Fmade by Miocare about the Chadderton
OL,11,FPark daycare centre.
OL,13,F"They are currently consulting with
OL,14,Fresidents and families to listen
OL,15,Fcarefully to their views and gather
OL,16,Ffeedback.
OL,18,F"The consultation is open until 2
OL,19,FMarch, and Miocare will not take any
OL,20,Fdecisions before then.
